§ VALIDATION  (reimpl-from-spec gate)

  § THESIS
    per §§ 23_TESTING + spec-validation-via-reimpl pattern, this
    Substrate-spec is reimpl-from-spec-validateable. divergence
    between phase-H impl + this doc = spec-hole, fix-doc-or-impl.

  § REIMPL-CONTRACTS  (W! impl-must-honor)
    R-1 : Omega type-shape exactly-matches § Ω-TENSOR § STRUCTURE.
          new-fields = spec-amendment ; rename = major-version-bump
          (per ABI-stability invariant from T11-D76).
    R-2 : omega_step signature matches § OMEGA-STEP § SIGNATURE.
          phase-order matches § PHASES table.
    R-3 : Projection type-shape matches § PROJECTIONS § STRUCTURE.
          ProjectionKind enum is-the-stable-set (ord-stable).
    R-4 : ConsentToken<dom> domain-set matches § Ω-TENSOR §
          OmegaConsent.
    R-5 : Effect-list { Sim Render Audio Net Save Replay } is the
          stage-0 stable-set ; new-effects = spec-amendment.
    R-6 : ω_halt() is single-canonical-kill-switch ;
          ¬-multiple-halt-paths.
    R-7 : audit-append failure ⇒ process-abort (mirroring §§ 22).
    R-8 : OmegaAttestation byte-identical-across-step.
    R-9 : @staged specialization on OmegaConfig produces
          deterministic per-config bit-exact omega_step.
    R-10 : ∀ test-mode @replay produces bit-exact-Ω-tensor on
            same-(attestation, consent, world, scene, sim, Δt, RNG).

  § ORACLE-MODES  (§§ 23_TESTING applied to Substrate)
    @replay              : omega_step×N bit-exact (R-10)
    @hot_reload_test     : Ω-tensor preserved across compatible-reload
    @audit_test          : audit-chain valid + signature-chain unbroken
    @power_bench         : omega_step under FRAME_BUDGET_MS @ POWER_BUDGET_W
    @thermal_stress      : sustained omega_step within THERMAL_LIMIT_C
    @differential        : omega_step on Vulkan ↔ Level-Zero ↔ Metal
                            bit-exact on {PureDet}-tagged paths
    @metamorphic         : ω_halt(t1, "x") ; ω_halt(t2, "x")  ⇒
                            second-call rejected at-type (linear-token)
    @property            : forall consent ∈ revoked-set,
                            omega_step skips matching-effects
    @golden              : Ω-tensor.serialized for known scenes
                            matches stored-snapshot (post-migration)
    @audit_test          : forbidden-effect-composition ⇒ compile-error
                            with expected-message
    @fuzz                : random Ω-tensor permutations + Δt sweep ⇒
                            no-panic, no-UB, audit-chain-intact

  § SMT-DISCHARGE  (§§ 20_SMT applied)
    Lipschitz-bounds on SDF-fields used by Sim/Render
    consent-token-active predicates verifiable
    refinement-types on Ω-tensor sub-fields (e.g. Δt > 0)
    cross-projection IFC-mask coverage (∀ visible-object ⊑ mask)
    {Verify<Z3>} obligations on @staged omega_step specializations

  § SUBSTRATE-PRIME-DIRECTIVE-ALIGNMENT (validation-level)
    cognitive-integrity : reimpl-from-spec catches drift before-merge ;
                          drift = bug-shape that-could-cause-hallucination
                          about-what-Substrate-does.
    no-deception : the spec is the contract. impl that diverges
                   without-spec-amendment = bad-faith. caught-by-tests.
    transparency : oracle-modes above are-exhaustive ; no-hidden-tests.

